label: The Rwenzori Times
title: The_Rwenzori_Times
exrest: The Rwenzori Times is an independent, first ever and biggest news website and magazine in Rwenzori region. The news website and magazine are owned and published by the Rwenzori Times Media Limited, with its offices and printing on Stanley Street, in the Central Town of Kasese, Uganda.
